      • MAX_SUPPORTED_CELLS_NUMBER

        static final Integer MAX_SUPPORTED_CELLS_NUMBER

      • MAX_SUPPORTED_ROWS_NUMBER

        static final Integer MAX_SUPPORTED_ROWS_NUMBER
